&lt;p&gt;Similarly, MAN will be written as &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;13114&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;, i.e&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;M &amp;rArr;13; A &amp;rArr;1; N &amp;rArr;14.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;option1)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to the given information we have:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Six students are sitting around a circular table facing the centre.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Step 1):&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Sonal (S) is sitting second to the right of Lavanya (L). Rana (R) is sitting second to the right of Sonal. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

