&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;3) Some T are B&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr;&amp;nbsp;Follow: Since some B are T and so some T are B is true.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

